 Object Detection DPC Configuration CommandsThis section has a list of all the commands which are supported by the DPC. All commands of the type IOCTL__STATIC_<...> can only be issued either before the first call to DPM_start (DPC_ObjectDetection_start) or after the DPM_stop (DPC_ObjectDetection_stop) All commands of the type IOCTL__DYNAMIC_<...> can be issued between at the inter-frame boundary i.e when the result is available from DPM_execute (DPC_ObjectDetection_execute). All commands of the type IOCTL__STATIC_<..> must be issued before DPM_start (DPC_ObjectDetection_start) because there are no defaults
 Object Detection DPC Error CodesThis section has a list of all the error codes returned when calling Object Detection DPC functions during error conditions
